{"tid":649190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(長文)終於知道點解咁多人娶大陸女人","createTime":"2018-05-01T11:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T11:49:17.000Z","uid":122600,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"550244ea1690a15156b77b4edfa941f68d5f9eec","tid":649190,"uid":122600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"話說我親戚有兩個朋友A，B<br />\nA係一個啱啱攞到三粒星身分證嘅大陸女人<br />\n喺隔離屋村有一個同樣係新移民嘅男友<br />\n密謀緊同自己本身個老野老公離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單啲講A即係假結婚嘅大陸婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nB係一個有啲錢嘅師奶<br />\n佢有個30中至尾嘅仔C，外型係比較老嘅毒男 唔識打扮為人木獨，冇女朋友<br />\n<br />\n而A同B原本互不相識<br />\n我親戚一直都知B想幫佢個仔搵老婆，又知A有大陸女人D介紹，咁就開始咗複雜嘅搭路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先C同D交換咗we7<br />\n但傾咩 send咩相A同B都完全知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始D睇到C張相，厭佢外表窮酸 冇打算發展 C仲同人報告D時冷時熱唔知有冇意思（睇到呢到，唔知大家有冇疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底點解一個30幾歲嘅人交友要不斷同老母報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上傾偈都唔識唔怪得要老母幫佢搵老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n佢地斷斷續續都有傾we7<br />\n有日D屎忽痕叫C影張相比佢睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢影咗啱沖完涼嘅自拍<br />\n結果呢件事又傳通晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畀人話咁大個人唔知醜blar blar blar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到咗最近，C話遲啲會嚟香港玩<br />\n打算約佢去迪士尼玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然呢個消息又傳開咗，B仲話要跟埋去同埋全家約C一齊飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最新消息係 D知道咗要見佢全家之後想縮沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但問題係佢嗰家人覺得冇問題 堅持要成家人去見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於明點解成日見到香港人同大陸女人結婚。部分唔識同人溝通，識唔到女又裙腳嘅人，到咗中年老母就會急住幫佢搵老婆，自然向有錢萬事足嘅大陸女人埋手<br />\n<br />\n同時，即使啲大陸女人口裡說不但心裡很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔覺香港有咩好但就猴住個男人啲錢同身分證，落嚟搵人埋單<br />\n而且A嘅背景都完全反映咗一啲大陸女人落嚟香港嘅計謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然都見過中港婚姻有真愛，唔可以排除呢個可能性嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"20ee893b20cd2e635b4be0c935153b3ba7e0ea84","tid":649190,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"我明，但大把白痴港嬸唔明<br />\n建議你去babycondom出文"},{"pid":"6e7f50f8626c46a61b88bc9873e40c74b195c259","tid":649190,"uid":44513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20ee893b20cd2e635b4be0c935153b3ba7e0ea84","tid":649190,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"我明，但大把白痴港嬸唔明<br />\n建議你去babycondom出文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"堆港媽比兩登更怕/憎內地女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7f4ecc8d20424da8a9f742c0d30412884408c9","tid":649190,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e7f50f8626c46a61b88bc9873e40c74b195c259","tid":649190,"uid":44513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20ee893b20cd2e635b4be0c935153b3ba7e0ea84","tid":649190,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"我明，但大把白痴港嬸唔明<br />\n建議你去babycondom出文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"堆港媽比兩登更怕/憎內地女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"咁真係要去啟晴德朗傳道"},{"pid":"165bcb909423a009af4edf80a197b04ae933f64a","tid":649190,"uid":2640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"打到1999咁<br />\nC話遲啲會嚟香港玩<br />\n<br />\nC唔係個香港師奶個仔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767274d62d1e3343accdd3046fb2862de0589d6b","tid":649190,"